Deprecated API

Contents

  • Deprecated Classes
  • Deprecated Methods
  • Deprecated Classes 
    Class and Description
    org.apache.datasketches.theta.PairwiseSetOperations
    v2.0.0. This class has been deprecated as equivalent functionality has been added to the SetOperation classes: Union, Intersection and AnotB.
  • Deprecated Methods 
    Method and Description
    org.apache.datasketches.theta.PairwiseSetOperations.aNotB(Sketch, Sketch)
    v2.0.0. Use AnotB.aNotB(Sketch, Sketch) instead, which has more complete seed handling.
    org.apache.datasketches.theta.Sketch.getCountLessThanTheta(double)
    v2.0.0. Use Sketch.getCountLessThanThetaLong(long). It is more accurate.
    org.apache.datasketches.theta.Sketch.getCurrentBytes(boolean)
    v2.0.0. use either Sketch.getCompactBytes() or Sketch.getCurrentBytes().
    org.apache.datasketches.tuple.SketchIterator.getKey()
    v2.0.0. Please use SketchIterator.getHash()
    org.apache.datasketches.kll.KllFloatsSketch.getNormalizedRankError()
    v2.0.0. Replaced by KllFloatsSketch.getNormalizedRankError(boolean)
    org.apache.datasketches.quantiles.DoublesSketch.getNormalizedRankError()
    v2.0.0. Replaced by DoublesSketch.getNormalizedRankError(boolean)
    org.apache.datasketches.quantiles.ItemsSketch.getNormalizedRankError()
    v2.0.0. Replaced by getNormalizedRankError(boolean)
    org.apache.datasketches.kll.KllFloatsSketch.getNormalizedRankError(int)
    v2.0.0. Replaced by KllFloatsSketch.getNormalizedRankError(int, boolean)
    org.apache.datasketches.quantiles.DoublesSketch.getNormalizedRankError(int)
    v2.0.0. Replaced by DoublesSketch.getNormalizedRankError(int, boolean)
    org.apache.datasketches.quantiles.ItemsSketch.getNormalizedRankError(int)
    v2.0.0. Replaced by getNormalizedRankError(int, boolean)
    org.apache.datasketches.tuple.AnotB.getResult()
    v2.0.0. Instead use AnotB.getResult(boolean).
    org.apache.datasketches.theta.AnotB.getResult()
    v2.0.0. Instead use AnotB.getResult(boolean) or AnotB.getResult(boolean, WritableMemory, boolean).
    org.apache.datasketches.theta.AnotB.getResult(boolean, WritableMemory)
    v2.0.0. Instead use AnotB.getResult(boolean) or AnotB.getResult(boolean, WritableMemory, boolean).
    org.apache.datasketches.quantiles.DoublesUnionBuilder.heapify(DoublesSketch)
    v2.0.0. Moved to DoublesUnion
    org.apache.datasketches.quantiles.DoublesUnionBuilder.heapify(Memory)
    v2.0.0. Moved to DoublesUnion
    org.apache.datasketches.theta.PairwiseSetOperations.intersect(Sketch, Sketch)
    v2.0.0. Use Intersection.intersect(Sketch, Sketch) instead, which has more complete seed handling.
    org.apache.datasketches.theta.PairwiseSetOperations.union(CompactSketch, CompactSketch)
    v2.0.0. Please use Union.union(Sketch, Sketch) instead, which has more complete seed handling.
    org.apache.datasketches.theta.PairwiseSetOperations.union(CompactSketch, CompactSketch, int)
    v2.0.0. Please use Union.union(Sketch, Sketch) instead, which has more complete seed handling.
    org.apache.datasketches.theta.Intersection.update(Sketch)
    v2.0.0. Use Intersection.intersect(Sketch) instead.
    org.apache.datasketches.tuple.AnotB.update(Sketch<S>, Sketch<S>)
    v2.0.0. Instead please use AnotB.aNotB(Sketch, Sketch).
    org.apache.datasketches.theta.AnotB.update(Sketch, Sketch)
    v2.0.0. Instead use AnotB.aNotB(Sketch, Sketch).
